WEBVTT

00:32.375 --> 00:34.000
Matsuda of Touto News.

00:34.083 --> 00:36.833
The public's attention
has been drawn by recent rumors

00:36.916 --> 00:39.625
of an incumbent minister
receiving payments

00:39.708 --> 00:42.541
in return for doing favors
for a certain construction company.

00:42.625 --> 00:44.541
Keep your questions brief.

00:44.625 --> 00:47.750
The minister contends
that his secretary did it.

00:47.833 --> 00:51.208
Are you sure it wasn't done
on the minister's orders?

00:51.291 --> 00:52.875
Please get to the point.

00:52.958 --> 00:56.333
The prime minister cannot avoid
being held indirectly responsible.

00:56.416 --> 00:58.250
What is the government's position on this?

00:58.333 --> 01:01.416
That is for the prime minister to decide.

01:12.875 --> 01:15.250
FREEDOM OF PRESS DETERIORATES
JAPAN RANKED 72ND, LOWEST IN G7

01:17.083 --> 01:18.125
<i>Report, position A.</i>

01:21.125 --> 01:22.958
Passengers are leaving soon.

01:24.000 --> 01:27.416
TERMINAL 2, NARITA INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT

01:29.458 --> 01:31.833
Suspect has just left the gate.

01:43.208 --> 01:45.000
Suspect passing position C now.

02:11.625 --> 02:13.000
Matsuda of Touto News.

02:13.083 --> 02:17.250
I'd like to ask another question
related to corruption in politics.

02:17.333 --> 02:19.291
It was recently revealed

02:19.375 --> 02:22.125
there was a misuse of funds from
the 2011 Earthquake Recovery Package.

02:22.208 --> 02:24.250
Keep your questions brief.

02:24.333 --> 02:26.333
PLANS FOR EISHIN ACADEMY
ELEMENTARY SCHOOL (TBC)

02:30.375 --> 02:31.541
What do you think?

02:31.625 --> 02:33.708
FINANCE BUREAU DIRECTOR-GENERAL'S OFFICE
MINISTRY OF FINANCE

02:34.208 --> 02:35.750
EISHIN ACADEMY EDUCATIONAL CORPORATION

02:38.041 --> 02:41.458
JUNE 2017: LECTURE AND TOUR BY FIRST LADY

02:42.291 --> 02:43.416
The First Lady's thoughts?

02:43.500 --> 02:45.833
She'd like it to go ahead officially.

02:46.333 --> 02:49.083
She knows the waste issue
still hasn't been resolved.

02:49.166 --> 02:54.041
But she says herself that the size
and suitability of the site is perfect.

02:56.125 --> 02:57.416
I'll need some time.

02:58.208 --> 03:00.291
I'll run this past
the Chubu Local Finance Bureau.

03:00.375 --> 03:02.833
Director-General,
please have a look at this.

03:06.958 --> 03:08.166
SHINICHI MURAKAMI

03:24.375 --> 03:25.625
What's this?

03:25.708 --> 03:28.458
Please consider it
a priority for your office.

03:29.166 --> 03:31.208
DEDUCTION OF APPROXIMATELY
1.222 BILLION YEN

03:31.291 --> 03:34.208
Surely, this deduction is far too much.

03:35.541 --> 03:37.125
It's the prime minister's wish.

03:39.000 --> 03:41.166
Suspect soon arriving
at the target location.

03:44.625 --> 03:47.958
-Yes?
<i>-The arrest of Toyoda was called off.</i>

03:48.041 --> 03:48.916
What?

03:49.000 --> 03:51.291
It was reported
that large contributions were paid

03:51.375 --> 03:54.416
by a corporation
that benefited from the project.

03:54.500 --> 03:56.291
What is the government's response?

03:56.375 --> 03:58.916
That is currently under investigation.

03:59.000 --> 04:01.333
The next question will be the last.

04:02.708 --> 04:03.875
Matsuda of Touto News.

04:03.958 --> 04:05.875
What? Why now?

04:05.958 --> 04:08.875
<i>At any rate,</i>
<i>do as you're ordered. Understand?</i>

04:10.916 --> 04:12.375
-We're moving in.
-Wait.

04:13.625 --> 04:16.500
-The arrest was called off.
-Why? He'll get away!

04:16.583 --> 04:19.208
How should I know?
The brass said to let him go.

04:19.291 --> 04:21.541
Let him go?
This is a ten-billion-yen fraud case!

04:24.416 --> 04:25.916
I appreciate your cooperation.

04:33.041 --> 04:34.416
<i>Matsuda of Touto News.</i>

04:34.500 --> 04:39.125
So I can assume that the results
of the investigation will be made public?

04:39.208 --> 04:42.625
Rather than just releasing information
favorable to the government,

04:42.708 --> 04:45.666
I'd like to see
impartial information released.

04:45.750 --> 04:48.833
This press conference
is not for you to air your opinions.

07:16.166 --> 07:17.416
I'm back.

07:17.500 --> 07:19.125
-Welcome back.
-Welcome back.

07:19.208 --> 07:20.041
-Thanks.
-Ryo.

07:20.125 --> 07:21.583
-Yes?
-Look at this.

07:21.666 --> 07:23.250
Another case of corruption.

07:23.333 --> 07:25.166
They said he took bribes.

07:25.250 --> 07:28.166
-Oh, I see.
-Is that any way to react?

07:28.250 --> 07:30.833
You'll start job hunting soon, you know.

07:30.916 --> 07:33.708
Start showing some interest
in social issues.

07:33.791 --> 07:37.708
The future depends on you guys,
the young people.

07:37.791 --> 07:40.125
Give me a break. That's asking too much.

07:40.208 --> 07:41.875
Asking too much?

07:41.958 --> 07:44.291
You've at least got to read the paper.

07:45.291 --> 07:48.041
Not a single young person
nowadays reads the paper.

07:48.125 --> 07:49.250
We've got smartphones.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.416
That's the trouble
with young people nowadays.

07:53.500 --> 07:54.916
Don't be ridiculous.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.958
You can do anything
with smartphones nowadays.

07:58.041 --> 07:59.000
Exactly.

07:59.083 --> 08:00.375
-Right?
-What?

08:00.875 --> 08:02.583
-See?
-I'm back.

08:02.666 --> 08:04.541
-Hi.
-Welcome back.

08:04.625 --> 08:07.333
-Good morning.
-Can you believe this, Mayu?

08:07.833 --> 08:11.166
Ryo doesn't read the paper
even though he works here.

08:12.750 --> 08:14.583
Really?

08:14.666 --> 08:16.750
What? You read it?

08:16.833 --> 08:18.291
You'd better believe it.

08:18.375 --> 08:21.208
How can you deliver it every day
and not be interested in it?

08:21.291 --> 08:24.708
But nobody I know reads it.

08:24.791 --> 08:26.458
Who cares what other people do?

08:26.958 --> 08:30.166
It's a waste of time to deliver newspapers
without knowing what's in them.

08:30.750 --> 08:33.208
Well put!

08:33.291 --> 08:36.125
-Be more like Mayu.
-That was a nice scolding.

08:37.458 --> 08:39.208
-I'm leaving.
-Are you mad, Ryo?

08:39.291 --> 08:40.291
No, I'm not.

08:41.166 --> 08:43.291
-Here. Have a tangerine.
-Thank you.

08:43.375 --> 08:46.125
-Are you mad?
-No, I'm not mad. Bye.

08:50.500 --> 08:51.875
Don't get mad.

09:07.708 --> 09:10.833
DUBIOUS DOCUMENTS
UNPROVEN EXISTENCE

09:10.916 --> 09:12.916
SHINJIRO TOYODA

09:27.375 --> 09:30.166
SHINJIRO TOYODA REVEALS
PM'S PRIVATE TRUE NATURE

09:49.916 --> 09:52.750
SHINPO AGENCY HEAD OFFICE

09:58.458 --> 10:00.916
Mr. Toyoda. Anna Matsuda of Touto News.

10:01.000 --> 10:02.583
May I have a moment?

10:03.458 --> 10:04.583
You again?

10:04.666 --> 10:06.333
